Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.76,0:12:48.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22\fad(0,2000)}欢迎光临热带天国
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.97,0:12:50.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在里面啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.73,0:12:52.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  没错
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.76,0:12:54.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  那就一鼓作气冲进去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.92,0:12:56.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  要冷静地进去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.14,0:12:58.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这话轮得到天城同学来说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.08,0:13:01.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之不能被热血冲昏头脑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.37,0:13:05.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我们的目的一是救出完二同学  二是救出完二同学
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.18,0:13:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千枝  你说的两个目的重复了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.45,0:13:09.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我是故意的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.42,0:13:11.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是故意的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.57,0:13:12.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给我注意到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.76,0:13:16.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天城的大脑构造真是让人无法理解啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.03,0:13:22.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不去开门呢熊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.92,0:13:25.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  总觉得…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.45,0:13:27.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算打开它也不会有什么好事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.72,0:13:30.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如说里面有恶心的景象在等着我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.28,0:13:31.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之可以想象得到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.05,0:13:34.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  但是我们该怎么办啊  鸣上同学
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.91,0:13:35.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放着不管吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.93,0:13:37.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说了那是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.45,0:13:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种时候就该由男生来打头阵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.94,0:13:40.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点快点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.02,0:13:42.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  为什么连我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.84,0:13:47.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊讨厌  不要啊  好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.12,0:13:47.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开什么玩笑啊  你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.06,0:13:49.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧  果然
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.10,0:13:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们为什么会出现在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.15,0:13:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.17,0:13:55.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们来救你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.22,0:13:57.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？  你那没精打采的回答算什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.86,0:13:58.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我推
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.30,0:14:01.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会让你们妨碍我的  哼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.11,0:14:07.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.98,0:14:09.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他以为用这种东西就能拖住我们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.02,0:14:11.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千枝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.16,0:14:13.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.91,0:14:15.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.55,0:14:16.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.30,0:14:17.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又黏又滑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.11,0:14:18.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.05,0:14:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站不起来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.62,0:14:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸣上  你有没有带什么可以摄像的东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.18,0:14:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶  没带
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.36,0:14:24.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在说些什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.11,0:14:26.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.75,0:14:29.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还是不要再欺骗自己了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.31,0:14:33.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做自己想要做的事情有什么不对
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.77,0:14:35.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是你的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.47,0:14:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.42,0:14:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停下  不要听  自来…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.45,0:14:41.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花村
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.57,0:14:44.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师  我现在就去救…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.89,0:14:47.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女人真讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.68,0:14:50.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一旦做针线活或者画画的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.84,0:14:54.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们就会嘲笑我「真恶心」「明明是个男人」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.16,0:14:57.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙  再不住口的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.84,0:15:01.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是个男人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.94,0:15:02.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是个男人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.96,0:15:04.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是个男人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.56,0:15:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常有男子汉气概又是怎么一回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.33,0:15:09.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女人真可怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.58,0:15:11.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点也不可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.35,0:15:12.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是男人好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.99,0:15:14.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少不会对我说「明明是个男人」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.31,0:15:17.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说男人就是好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.51,0:15:18.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.43,0:15:19.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可没说错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.98,0:15:22.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是我  我就是你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.86,0:15:24.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.73,0:15:26.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  不要说啊完二
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.54,0:15:29.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这种家伙怎么可能是我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.34,0:15:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是你  是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.70,0:15:41.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾即为影  是为真实的自我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.51,0:15:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别在那里胡扯了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.17,0:15:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最讨厌别人妨碍我了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.20,0:15:50.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完二君
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.74,0:15:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.35,0:15:52.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.00,0:15:55.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想坦诚面对自我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.07,0:15:58.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以碍事的家伙们就请消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.83,0:16:00.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这居然是完二君的真心话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.86,0:16:02.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这才不是什么真心话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.42,0:16:04.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不过是他性格的阴暗面暴走了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.68,0:16:05.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要上了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.42,0:16:13.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Come on Baby
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.34,0:16:14.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.25,0:16:18.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.63,0:16:19.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.92,0:16:20.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.23,0:16:23.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂熊熊  这是怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.42,0:16:24.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对面怎么混进了奇怪的家伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.75,0:16:28.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概这些家伙也是完二的Shadow中的一部分熊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.10,0:16:31.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  真是个好男人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.24,0:16:32.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用…用Change来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.27,0:16:34.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.70,0:16:44.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hold me tight
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.96,0:16:45.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chan…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.50,0:16:49.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想吃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.01,0:16:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了熊  他们的精神被摧残了熊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.64,0:16:59.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了  男生被干掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.49,0:17:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系  他对我们没兴趣的…应该
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.64,0:17:04.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.32,0:17:06.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.58,0:17:08.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下流的红色
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.35,0:17:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再多加把劲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.12,0:17:16.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静点  雪子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.32,0:17:20.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干…干嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.56,0:17:26.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你倒是给我说句话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.40,0:17:32.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Feel so good
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.37,0:17:35.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都冷静点啊熊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.81,0:17:38.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼哼  你们根本没什么了不起的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.15,0:17:40.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是笑死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.21,0:17:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,充满热情的声音  这心中那止不住的悸动
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.52,0:17:55.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可真碍眼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.89,0:18:05.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.19,0:18:13.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  最后的高潮时间
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.86,0:18:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.78,0:18:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们恭候您多时了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.40,0:18:31.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人所拥有的「Wild」的真正力量  它的觉醒之刻终于到来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.95,0:18:57.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.01,0:18:59.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合而为一了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.78,0:19:05.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不讨厌  我一点也不讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.34,0:19:06.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好火热啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.26,0:19:10.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.53,0:19:12.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.44,0:19:15.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.99,0:19:17.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是你做的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.02,0:19:20.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了啊  不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.22,0:19:23.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身为男人居然还做这种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.64,0:19:25.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我觉得很可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.55,0:19:28.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.80,0:19:29.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.59,0:19:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可可可可爱？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.91,0:19:36.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可可可可可爱  可爱的东西最棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.06,0:19:45.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可真是纠缠不清
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.38,0:19:48.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  没错
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.10,0:19:49.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.75,0:19:53.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是喜欢可爱的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.80,0:19:55.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.38,0:20:01.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接受我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.10,0:20:05.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亲手把自己的Shadow打倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.64,0:20:10.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…我觉得很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.13,0:20:12.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能称赞这个东西很可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.48,0:20:14.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能够认同我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.98,0:20:22.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他还在向这边走啊熊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.31,0:20:24.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说遭到了相当强烈的排斥吗熊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.34,0:20:28.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不论是谁都行  接受我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.93,0:20:31.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接受我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.35,0:20:33.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都说了不要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.41,0:20:39.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真丢人  没想到我的心中居然有这样的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.67,0:20:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完二
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.38,0:20:43.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和是男是女没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.57,0:20:45.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只是害怕被拒绝而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.47,0:20:49.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是个故意去惹人讨厌的没种混蛋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.29,0:20:52.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我早就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.52,0:20:55.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是我  我就是你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.59,0:20:57.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个混帐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.02,0:21:09.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是完二君的Persona
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.50,0:21:11.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有男子汉气概
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.54,0:21:20.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Persona
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.43,0:21:23.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧  完二
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.17,0:21:23.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.87,0:21:24.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完二
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.58,0:21:24.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完二君…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.05,0:21:40.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做出这种东西来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.81,0:21:44.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然不论是男是女都会觉得不舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.97,0:21:48.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了  那种事已经无所谓了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.88,0:21:49.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.07,0:21:51.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托您的福
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.43,0:21:53.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说你还用敬语啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.69,0:21:55.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你们就像我的学长一样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.33,0:22:00.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起这些  究竟是谁把我扔进电视里去的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.86,0:22:03.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们正在寻找这个人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.03,0:22:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搜捕犯人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.94,0:22:08.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件事可以算上我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.69,0:22:11.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中了别人的招以后不十倍奉还的话我就解不了气
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.51,0:22:13.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.53,0:22:14.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他可是一大战斗力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.87,0:22:16.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  可以吧  鸣上同学
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.35,0:22:18.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.30,0:22:19.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.24,0:22:22.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本人巽完二  愿为学长们赴汤蹈火  在所不辞
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.34,0:23:37.38,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c000000}人之间的羁绊就是真正的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.23,0:23:41.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听足立说了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.35,0:23:45.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们好像去过巽家的染坊了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.90,0:23:47.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们去那里干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.54,0:23:49.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陪朋友办点事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.25,0:23:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没有参与什么奇怪的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.28,0:23:58.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵架？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.22,0:24:00.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  只是在聊天而已
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.50,0:24:01.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.72,0:24:02.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  这个很好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.54,0:24:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(276,187)\1c000000\bord0\shad0\b1}两天前
